HEADWORD: Genevese
<hw>Gen`e*vese"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. L.
<ets>Genevensis</ets>, F. <ets>g⟦eacute⟧nevois</ets>.]</ety> <def>Of or
